result: Queestion 85) So said, “This is where I will build. Everything can get here by Euphrates, the tiager and a network of chaannels. Only a place like this will support the army and the general population. ” Thus he traded and destined the funds for his construction, and laid the first brick with his own hand, saying, “In the name of God, and in praise to Him. I built, and may God bless you. ”
